139
140/* RSA_additional_prime contains information about the third, forth etc prime
141 * in a multi-prime RSA key. */
142typedef struct RSA_additional_prime_st {
143 BIGNUM *prime;
144 /* exp is d^{prime-1} mod prime */
145 BIGNUM *exp;
146 /* coeff is such that r×coeff ≡ 1 mod prime. */
147 BIGNUM *coeff;
148
149 /* Values below here are not in the ASN.1 serialisation. */
150
151 /* r is the product of all primes (including p and q) prior to this one. */
152 BIGNUM *r;
153 /* mont is a |BN_MONT_CTX| modulo |prime|. */
154 BN_MONT_CTX *mont;
155} RSA_additional_prime;
156
157void RSA_additional_prime_free(RSA_additional_prime *ap);
